{"data":{"properties":{"created_at":1632104977000,"events":{},"identifier":"layouts/stack","modified_at":1632104977000,"properties":{"Stack":[{"name":"orientation","description":"<p>Renders the <code>Stack</code> horizontally.</p>\n","types":["horizontal","{VIEWPORT}:horizontal"]},{"name":"alignment","description":"<p>Adjusts where the child items will be placed within the <code>Stack</code> along both axis.</p>\n","types":["center","stretch","{VIEWPORT}:{ALIGNMENT}"]},{"name":"alignment_x","description":"<p>Adjusts where the child items will be placed within the <code>Stack</code> along the horizontal axis.</p>\n","types":["center","stretch","left","right","{VIEWPORT}:{ALIGNMENT}"]},{"name":"alignment_y","description":"<p>Adjusts where the child items will be placed within the <code>Stack</code> along the vertical axis.</p>\n","types":["center","stretch","bottom","top","{VIEWPORT}:{ALIGNMENT}"]},{"name":"spacing","description":"<p>Adjusts the visual spacing between child items in the <code>Stack</code>.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge","{VIEWPORT}:{SPACING}"]},{"name":"spacing_x","description":"<p>Adjusts the horizontal visual spacing between child items in the <code>Stack</code>.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge","{VIEWPORT}:{SPACING}"]},{"name":"spacing_y","description":"<p>Adjusts the vertical visual spacing between child items in the <code>Stack</code>.</p>\n","types":["tiny","small","medium","large","huge","{VIEWPORT}:{SPACING}"]}]},"sections":[{"identifier":"stack","level":1,"text":"Stack"},{"identifier":"imports","level":2,"text":"Imports"},{"identifier":"orientation","level":2,"text":"Orientation"},{"identifier":"spacing","level":2,"text":"Spacing"},{"identifier":"alignment","level":2,"text":"Alignment"},{"identifier":"wrap","level":2,"text":"Wrap"}],"snippets":[{"identifier":"stack-preview","script":"<script>\n    import {Box, Stack} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack class=\"stack-preview\">\n    <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n    <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n    <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.stack-preview .box) {\n        width: 3rem;\n        height: 3rem;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Stack Preview"},{"identifier":"stack-imports","script":"<script>\n    import {Stack} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>","syntax":"html","title":"Stack Imports"},{"identifier":"stack-orientation","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Box,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"stack-orientation\"\n    alignment_y=\"top\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack>\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">HORIZONTAL</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Stack orientation=\"horizontal\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.stack-orientation .stack .box) {\n        width: 3rem;\n        height: 3rem;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Stack Orientation"},{"identifier":"stack-spacing","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Box,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"stack-spacing\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack>\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">TINY</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack spacing=\"tiny\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">SMALL</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack spacing=\"small\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">MEDIUM</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack spacing=\"medium\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">LARGE</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack spacing=\"large\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">HUGE</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack spacing=\"huge\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.stack-spacing .stack .box) {\n        width: 3rem;\n        height: 3rem;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Stack Spacing"},{"identifier":"stack-alignment","script":"<script>\n    import {\n        Box,\n        Stack,\n        Text,\n    } from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"stack-alignment\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"medium\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">DEFAULT</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack>\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">CENTER X/Y</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Stack alignment=\"center\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">STRETCH X</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Stack alignment_x=\"stretch\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">LEFT X</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Stack alignment_x=\"left\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">RIGHT X</Text>\n        <Box palette=\"dark\" padding=\"small\">\n            <Stack alignment_x=\"right\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">TOP Y</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack alignment_y=\"top\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n        <Text is=\"strong\">BOTTOM Y</Text>\n        <Box\n            palette=\"dark\"\n            padding=\"small\"\n            width=\"content-min\"\n        >\n            <Stack alignment_y=\"bottom\">\n                <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n                <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n                <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n            </Stack>\n        </Box>\n    </div>\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.stack-alignment .stack .box) {\n        min-width: 3rem;\n        min-height: 3rem;\n    }\n\n    :global(.stack-alignment\n            .stack[data-alignment~=\"center\"]) {\n        width: 6rem;\n        height: 12rem;\n    }\n\n    :global(.stack-alignment\n            .stack[data-alignment-x~=\"stretch\"]) {\n        width: 6rem;\n        height: 12rem;\n    }\n\n    :global(.stack-alignment\n            .stack[data-alignment-x~=\"left\"]),\n    :global(.stack-alignment\n            .stack[data-alignment-x~=\"right\"]) {\n        width: 6rem;\n    }\n\n    :global(.stack-alignment\n            .stack[data-alignment-y~=\"top\"]),\n    :global(.stack-alignment\n            .stack[data-alignment-y~=\"bottom\"]) {\n        height: 12rem;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Stack Alignment"},{"identifier":"stack-wrap","script":"<script>\n    import {Box, Stack} from \"@kahi-ui/framework\";\n</script>\n\n<Stack\n    class=\"stack-wrap\"\n    orientation=\"horizontal\"\n    spacing=\"huge\"\n    variation=\"wrap\"\n>\n    <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n    <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n    <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n\n    <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n    <Box palette=\"affirmative\" />\n    <Box palette=\"negative\" />\n\n    <Box palette=\"alert\" />\n</Stack>\n\n<style>\n    :global(.stack-wrap .box) {\n        width: 6rem;\n        height: 6rem;\n    }\n</style>","syntax":"svelte","title":"Stack Wrap"}],"title":"Stack"},"render":"<h1 id=\"stack\">Stack</h1>\n<p><code>Stack</code> is a layout primitive for setting up a horizontal / vertical stacking of items with even spacing between children. With optional wrapping.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-preview?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-preview?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"imports\">Imports</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-html snippet-highlight\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>Stack<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"@kahi-ui/framework\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre><h2 id=\"orientation\">Orientation</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsivity\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>orientation={[&quot;desktop:horizontal&quot;, &quot;widescreen:horizontal&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can set the <code>Stack</code> to render horizontally via the <code>orientation</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-orientation?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-orientation?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"spacing\">Spacing</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsivity\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>spacing={[&quot;medium&quot;, &quot;tablet:small&quot;, &quot;mobile:tiny&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can adjust the spacing between items via the <code>spacing</code>, <code>spacing_x</code>, and <code>spacing_y</code> properties.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-spacing?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-spacing?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"alignment\">Alignment</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsivity\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>alignment_x={[&quot;center&quot;, &quot;tablet:left&quot;, &quot;mobile:right&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can adjust the spacing between items via the <code>alignment</code>, <code>alignment_x</code>, and <code>alignment_y</code> properties.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-alignment?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-alignment?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"wrap\">Wrap</h2>\n<p>You can alter the <code>Stack</code> to wraps its children into the next line via the <code>variation</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-wrap?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/layouts/stack/stack-wrap?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}